details.name: Tile 2,-8
details.description:
The first boss pet your team receives will instantly clear the tile you are on, as long as the boss in involved in the tile. Any future boss pets will count as 1x unique towards that tile.

 

If you recieve the boss pet and you only have 1x unique left to get, this will not use your auto-complete bonus and will instead count for 1x unique, meaning your next boss pet will clear the tile.

 

Example:

Team 1 are on the Cerberus tile, and have 1 Unique left to get to clear it and they get the boss pet. This counts as 1x unique only and team 1 retain their boss pet bonus.

 

Team 2 are also on Cerberus with 0/3 drops. They get the boss pet, instantly clearing the tile. They have now used their boss pet bonus and future pets count as 1x unique only.

 

Exceptions:

  • Obtaining a pet from Wintertodt, Tempoross or Zalcano will not auto complete your KC count for the gauge.
  • Stackable boss pets such as Jad, Nibbler and Smol Heridit are not included, unless the pet is from the KC completion. Trading in Capes/Quivers do not count.
